taff and budget, an unfortunate consequence of Cond=C3=A9=E2=80=99s revenue=
 challenges. Like much of the grunt work at this company, the onus somehow =
fell on Wintour, the keeper of what=E2=80=99s left of Cond=C3=A9 Nast=E2=80=
=99s flame, to clean up the mess. (The company has yet to hire a replacemen=
t for Olden.)

Things are destined to
grow more intense as autumn progresses and concerns around potential layoff=
s bubble up once again. Next Tuesday, new chief revenue officer Elizabeth H=
erbst-Brady will host her first revenue summit, which I=E2=80=99m told was =
whittled down from two days to one day by Herbst-Brady, herself. (I heard t=
